Description: A serverless, highly scalable, and cost-effective cloud data warehouse designed to help you make informed decisions quickly, so you can transform your business with ease.
Name: Google BigQuery

Methods.Name: List Projects
Methods.Description: List projects to which the user has been granted any project role.

Methods.Name: List Datasets
Methods.Description: Lists all datasets in the specified project to which the user has been granted the READER dataset role.

Methods.Name: Update Dataset
Methods.Description: Update an existing dataset by overwriting existing fields with fields supplied.

Methods.Name: List Tables
Methods.Description: Lists all tables in the specified dataset. Requires the READER dataset role.

Methods.Name: List Table Data
Methods.Description: List the content of a table in rows.

Methods.Name: List New Table Data
Methods.Description: List the content of a table in rows added since the last run.

Methods.Name: List Partial Table Data
Methods.Description: List the content of a specific rows of a table

Methods.Name: Get Query Results
Methods.Description: Get the results of a query job.

Methods.Name: Create Query
Methods.Description: Runs a BigQuery SQL query synchronously and returns query results if the query completes within a specified timeout.
